blog.name: orion-sprinkles-stardust
blog.title: Orion’s Recycling Bin
blog.description:
| Orion or Exo |💜She/Her/Hers💜| This account was turned into an art blog for the new year! I’ll have my activism and fandom accounts up sometime soon and I’ll compile them in a master list when I’ve made them. Comms are closed until I have a payment method but requests are open and I’ll draw anything from a fandom I’m part of (Harry Potter, Percy Jackson, FMA, Hetalia [I promise I’m not one of the cringey people in this fandom], Voltron, Gravity Falls, Thomas Sanders, and there’s probably much more I’m forgetting), and soon I’ll be taking comms for OC’s. The only things I won’t draw are things like incest, pedophilia, kink, non-con and sexual NSFW, but I’m fine with violence and gore. Stay tuned for a post about which fandoms I take requests for and all the pricings for my comms!

Art Instagram: @/warrior_moonrider
